{"tid":2169753,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大愈唔識同人熟","createTime":"2020-08-22T17:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T17:13:15.000Z","uid":103044,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"29c496c21438c61d4d1f8303db5f53fd339efc3d","tid":2169753,"uid":103044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:47:40.000Z","msg":"我發覺我好似係邊到都揾唔到歸屬感。<br />\n<br />\n讀大學既時候，讀果科比較competitive, 啲同學好勢利，搞到自己都唔敢再show自己on99果面。同同學關係ok, 但冇咩真係好熟既人。<br />\n<br />\n出嚟做野後，公司啲同事多女人，好多是非，唔想埋堆，搞到冇咩歸屬感。<br />\n<br />\n本身自己都有跟球隊打波，啲隊友都nice, 年紀都差唔多，但唔知點解就熟唔到。<br />\n<br />\n人愈大愈唔識同人熟咁，好驚會得罪人。我以前份人鐘意周圍玩，宜家變到好悶、好正經咁。我有d唔係咁鐘意咁樣既自己...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1daa666ada944352e5474a30726d2858c9579c43","tid":2169753,"uid":339751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:49:20.000Z","msg":"識下啲癲啲既朋友<br />\n一齊出去玩啲癲野 會開心好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4b19ccb59904ff055f21662bba4d4531f1369e","tid":2169753,"uid":103044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1daa666ada944352e5474a30726d2858c9579c43","tid":2169753,"uid":339751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:49:20.000Z","msg":"識下啲癲啲既朋友<br />\n一齊出去玩啲癲野 會開心好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:50:41.000Z","msg":"唔知點識 同埋好似唔識埋堆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503ffc5d3adc33132d2fd8b6fa736e83bac1cfae","tid":2169753,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:51:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭西"},{"pid":"fedfe2c766a35ff62f5c2ac7851cb797d6815bfb","tid":2169753,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad4b19ccb59904ff055f21662bba4d4531f1369e","tid":2169753,"uid":103044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1daa666ada944352e5474a30726d2858c9579c43","tid":2169753,"uid":339751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"sc